{"types":[{"section":"\n{{head|fr|conjunction}} {{i|+ {{lg|subjunctive}}}}\n\n# let's hope (that)\n#: {{ux|fr|'''Pourvu qu''''il arrive à temps ! J'ai pas envie de rater le train.|'''Let's hope''' that he arrives on time! I don't want to miss the train.}}\n# [[provided]] (that), [[as long as]]\n#: {{syn|fr|tant que}}\n#: {{ux|fr|Je suis d'accord de te payer ton billet d'avion, '''pourvu que''' tu réussisses tes examens.|I'm okay with buying you a plane ticket, '''provided that''' you pass your exams.}}\n\n","alt":[],"syn":["tant que"],"type":"conjunction","html":"<p><span class=\"headword-line\"><strong class=\"Latn headword\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/pourvu#French\" title=\"pourvu\">pourvu</a> <a href=\"/wiki/que#French\" title=\"que\">que</a></strong></span> <span class=\"ib-brac qualifier-brac\">(</span><span class=\"ib-content qualifier-content\">+ <a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Glossary#subjunctive\" title=\"Appendix:Glossary\">subjunctive</a></span><span class=\"ib-brac qualifier-brac\">)</span>\n</p><ol><li>let's hope (that)\n<dl><dd><div class=\"h-usage-example\"><i class=\"Latn mention e-example\" lang=\"fr\"><b>Pourvu qu'</b>il arrive à temps ! J'ai pas envie de rater le train.</i><dl><dd><span class=\"e-translation\"><b>Let's hope</b> that he arrives on time! I don't want to miss the train.</span></dd></dl></div></dd></dl></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/provided\" title=\"provided\">provided</a> (that), <a href=\"/wiki/as_long_as\" title=\"as long as\">as long as</a>\n<dl><dd><span class=\"nyms synonym\"><span class=\"defdate\">Synonym:</span> <span class=\"Latn\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/tant_que#French\" title=\"tant que\">tant que</a></span></span></dd>\n<dd><div class=\"h-usage-example\"><i class=\"Latn mention e-example\" lang=\"fr\">Je suis d'accord de te payer ton billet d'avion, <b>pourvu que</b> tu réussisses tes examens.</i><dl><dd><span class=\"e-translation\">I'm okay with buying you a plane ticket, <b>provided that</b> you pass your exams.</span></dd></dl></div></dd></dl></li></ol>","trans":["let's hope","provided , as long as"]}],"title":"pourvu que","id":"690806","audios":[{"name":"Fr-pourvu que.ogg","url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/1c/Fr-pourvu_que.ogg"}],"ipas":["/puʁ.vy kə/"],"pronunSection":"\n* {{fr-IPA}}\n* {{audio|fr|Fr-pourvu que.ogg}}\n\n","pronunHtml":"<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Wiktionary:International_Phonetic_Alphabet\" title=\"Wiktionary:International Phonetic Alphabet\">IPA</a><sup>(<a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:French_pronunciation\" title=\"Appendix:French pronunciation\">key</a>)</sup>: <span class=\"IPA\">/puʁ.vy kə/</span></li>\n<li><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r50165410\">.mw-parser-output .k-player .k-attribution{visibility:hidden}</style><table class=\"audiotable\" style=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>Audio<span class=\"ib-colon qualifier-colon\">:</span></td><td class=\"audiofile\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><span><audio id=\"mwe_player_0\" controls=\"\" preload=\"none\" data-mw-tmh=\"\" class=\"mw-file-element\" width=\"175\" style=\"\" data-durationhint=\"2\" data-mwtitle=\"Fr-pourvu_que.ogg\" data-mwprovider=\"wikimediacommons\"><source src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/1c/Fr-pourvu_que.ogg\" type=\"audio/ogg; codecs=&quot;vorbis&quot;\" data-width=\"0\" data-height=\"0\"><source src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/transcoded/1/1c/Fr-pourvu_que.ogg/Fr-pourvu_que.ogg.mp3\" type=\"audio/mpeg\" data-transcodekey=\"mp3\" data-width=\"0\" data-height=\"0\"></audio></span></span></td><td class=\"audiometa\" style=\"\">(<a href=\"/wiki/File:Fr-pourvu_que.ogg\" title=\"File:Fr-pourvu que.ogg\">file</a>)</td></tr></tbody></table></li></ul>"}